<h1>マルチメディア</h1>
</header><article class="si-teaser beat--economy" >
<p class="si-teaser__label">おすすめの記事</p> <a class="si-teaser__link" href="/jpn/multimedia/%E3%83%95%E3%83%A9%E3%83%B3%E3%82%B9-%E3%83%AF%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B1%E3%83%BC%E3%82%B7%E3%83%A7%E3%83%B3-%E4%BD%93%E9%A8%93%E8%AB%87/45932130">
<div class="si-teaser__image">
<picture>
<source srcset="/resource/image/45933726/landscape_ratio3x2/280/186/8bc850ff193a3484618df27d1db80503/cf/200728_pack_and_work-jp_2.jpg" media="(min-width: 600px)">
<source srcset="/resource/image/45933726/landscape_ratio3x2/280/186/8bc850ff193a3484618df27d1db80503/cf/200728_pack_and_work-jp_2.jpg" media="(max-width: 320px)">
